00309 static XED_INLINE xed_uint32_t xed_inst_get_attribute(const xed_inst_t* p, xed_attribute_enum_t attr) {
00310     const xed_uint64_t one = 1;
00311     if (p->_attributes & (one<<attr)) 
00312         return 1;
00313     return 0;
00314 }
